.Dd May 17, 2026
.Dt DOOMMENU 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm doommenu
.Nd DOOMSDAY menu module
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is the named DOOMSDAY module for the customized
.Xr dmenu 1
build. It is installed as part of
.Fl -wm
because the window-manager workflow uses it for launching commands and driving
desktop actions.
.Sh INSTALL
.Dl \&./install.sh --wm
.Sh INSTALLED COMMANDS
.Bl -tag -width "dmenu_path"
.It Nm dmenu
Dynamic menu executable.
.It Nm dmenu_run
Launcher helper.
.It Nm dmenu_path
Path cache helper.
.It Nm stest
File-test helper used by dmenu scripts.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr doomsday-system 1 ,
.Xr verydynamicwindowmanager 1 ,
.Xr dmenu 1
